text: Possum Walk Creek (also called Possum Branch) is a stream in Audrain County in the U.S. state of Missouri. It is a tributary of Mayes Branch. Possum Walk Creek was named for the abundance of opossums along its course. ==See also== *List of rivers of Missouri ==References== Category:Rivers of Audrain County, Missouri Category:Rivers of Missouri
title: Possum Walk Creek (Mayes Branch tributary)
